title: Contact speed dial
content: I just added a contact to my phone's start screen for speed dial. I had a photo of the contact on the contact record and it appears as the speed dial Icon on the start page, but there is also the little blue man icon low and at about 5 O'clock on the contact photo. Why is that generic contact icon there?
category: Contacts, Calls, Voicemail, Google Pixel 3 XL
